name: Yosapp-api
tagline: Web API for Whatsapp written in Python
body:
### Welcome to Yosapp API.
API for Yosapp.com (http://folksfreak.github.io/yosapp). This is a web port of [tgalal's Yowsup](https://github.com/tgalal/yowsup).

### Authors and Contributors
Spreading the openness from folksFreak.
